Text: I love you slicknick610. Not in a gay way.

Nick, thank you so much from the Netherlands. You make a lot of supercross and motocross fans all over the world really really happy!! Amazing quality, uploaded very soon after the air date on television. Hopefully you'll continue to do so for a loooooooong time! Thank you.
